Description: Desktop Prayer Times App
 A desktop prayer times application for Linux built using GTK 4 and
 Libadwaita. It runs in the background, displays prayer timetables,
 and alerts you when it is time to pray.
 .
 Features prayer times from Aladhan API and Kemenag (MyQuran ID),
 system tray indicator with countdown, desktop notifications,
 bilingual support (Indonesian/English), and autostart option.
